'''格利泽436b'''（{{lang en|'''Gliese 436 b'''}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|ɡ|l|iː|z|ə}}）是一個環繞[[格利泽436|格利泽436]]的[[太陽系外行星|系外]][[氣體巨行星|氣體巨行星]]，其大小與[[海王星|海王星]]差不多。由於離母恆星非常的近，故其表面溫度很高，達712 K（439 °C）。有趣的是，雖然格利泽436b的表面溫度極高，但是其內部[[氣壓|氣壓]]非常大，因此其表面上的水蒸氣會凝結成[[冰|冰]]或[[水|水]]。<ref name="hot ice">{{cite news| publisher=New Scientist| url=http://space.newscientist.com/article/dn11864-strange-alien-world-made-of-hot-ice-and-steam.html| title=Strange alien world made of "hot ice"| date=6 May 2007| first=David| last=Shiga| accessdate=2007-05-16| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080706143705/http://space.newscientist.com/article/dn11864-strange-alien-world-made-of-hot-ice-and-steam.html| archive-date=2008-07-06| dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==發現==
格利澤436b是於2004年8月被華盛頓卡內基研究所的{{link-en|R·保羅·巴特勒|R. Paul Butler}}和[[加州大學|加州大學]]的[[史蒂文·沃格特|史蒂文·沃格特]]發現，他們是使用[[徑向速度|徑向速度測量法]]發現這顆行星的。同時，他們亦發現了[[巨蟹座55e|巨蟹座55e]]。這兩顆行星是首批被發現的系外類海王星行星，即[[冰巨星|冰巨星]]。

於2005年1月11日，[[新墨西哥州立大學|新墨西哥州立大學]]的自動巡天系統透過凌日法發現了這顆行星，但這個發現沒有受到重視。<ref name=coughlin>{{cite journal|title=New observations and a possible detection of parameter variations in the transits of Gliese 436b| year=2008|last1=Coughlin | first1=Jeffrey L.|last2=Stringfellow | first2=Guy S.|last3=Becker | first3=Andrew C.|author4=Mercedes Lopez-Morales|author5=Fabio Mezzalira|author6=Tom Krajci|doi=10.1086/595822|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|volume=689|issue=2|pages=L149–L152| arxiv=0809.1664 | bibcode=2008ApJ...689L.149C}}</ref>於2007年，吉隆帶領著一個觀察了行星凌日的團隊，並透過再次測量凌日，計算出其精確的質量和半徑數據，並發現這顆行星與海王星非常相似。在當時，格利泽436b成為了透過凌日法發現的體積最小的行星。這顆行星的直徑比[[天王星|天王星]]長約4000公里，比海王星長約5000公里，且質量稍比海王星高。其半長軸長4,000,000公里，比[[水星|水星]]的半長軸短15倍。

==物理特性==
[[File:GJ436interior.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Exoplanet_Comparison_Gliese_436_b.png|250px]]

因為與母星的距離過於接近，格利澤436b的表面溫度被母星加熱至712 K（439 °C），因此是一個[[熱海王星|熱海王星]]。<ref name="deming">{{cite journal|title=Spitzer Transit and Secondary Eclipse Photometry of GJ 436b|year=2007|author1=Drake Deming|author2=Joseph Harrington|author3=Gregory Laughlin|author4=Sara Seager|last5=Navarro | first5=Sarah B.|last6=Bowman | first6=William C.|author7=Karen Horning|doi=10.1086/522496|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|volume=667|issue=2|pages=L199–L202|arxiv=0707.2778|bibcode=2007ApJ...667L.199D}}</ref>天文學家相信如此高溫並不可能僅僅被恆星輻射加熱就可達到，而是加上潮汐效應才達到的。<ref>{{cite journal| title=Tidal Heating of Extra-Solar Planets|year=2008| author1=Brian Jackson| author2=Richard Greenberg| author3=Rory Barnes| doi=10.1086/587641| journal=The Astrophysical Journal| volume=681| issue=2| pages=1631–1638 |arxiv=0803.0026| bibcode=2008ApJ...681.1631J}}</ref>而且，溫室效應亦會導致溫度升高，如[[金星|金星]]。<ref name=gillon>{{cite journal | url=http://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/pdf/2007/35/aa7799-07.pdf | title=Detection of transits of the nearby hot Neptune GJ 436 b | author=M. Gillon ''et al.'' | journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume=472 | year=2007 | page=L13–L16 | format=PDF | bibcode=2007A&A...472L..13G | doi=10.1051/0004-6361:20077799 | issue=2 | arxiv=0705.2219 | access-date=2013-12-15 | archive-date=2020-10-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021132120/https://www.aanda.org/articles/aa/pdf/2007/35/aa7799-07.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>

儘管其表面溫度極高，但[[冰|冰]]仍能存在於這顆行星上。這些「冰」是因為高壓壓縮而成<ref name=gillon /><ref name="hot ice">{{cite news| publisher=New Scientist| url=http://space.newscientist.com/article/dn11864-strange-alien-world-made-of-hot-ice-and-steam.html| title=Strange alien world made of "hot ice"| date=6 May 2007| first=David| last=Shiga| accessdate=2007-05-16| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080706143705/http://space.newscientist.com/article/dn11864-strange-alien-world-made-of-hot-ice-and-steam.html| archive-date=2008-07-06| dead-url=yes}}</ref>，而這是因行星本身的強引力所致。<ref>{{cite news | title = Hot "ice" may cover recently discovered planet | first = Maggie | last = Fox | publisher = Scientific American.com | work = Science News | date = May 16, 2007 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/scienceNews/idUSN1621607620070516 | accessdate = 2008-08-06 | archive-date = 2020-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201011192115/https://www.reuters.com/article/scienceNews/idUSN1621607620070516 | dead-url = no }}</ref>這顆行星很可能在距離母星更遠的地方形成，並且原本是一個[[氣體巨行星|類木行星]]，但後來逐漸接近母星後，其表面厚厚的氫氣大氣被[[日冕物质抛射|日冕物质抛射]]吹走，才變成現今的模樣。<ref>{{cite journal | journal=Geophysical Research Abstracts | volume=9 | issue=07850 | year=2007 | url=http://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EGU2007/07850/EGU2007-J-07850.pdf?PHPSESSID=1eb3a7a98603083dda25d18001ea2a33 | title=The impact of nonthermal loss processes on planet masses from Neptunes to Jupiters | author=H. Lammer ''et al.'' | access-date=2013-12-15 | archive-date=2019-12-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191215090631/https://www.cosis.net/abstracts/EGU2007/07850/EGU2007-J-07850.pdf?PHPSESSID=1eb3a7a98603083dda25d18001ea2a33 | dead-url=no }} By analogy with [[Gliese_876_d|Gliese 876 d]].</ref>

然而，隨著其半徑逐漸為人所理解，冰便不足以構成整顆行星。在冰上，浮著佔總質量10%的[[氫氣|氫氣]]和[[氦氣|氦氣]]。<ref name="deming" /><ref name="bean">{{Cite journal|url=http://www.aanda.org/index.php?option=article&access=standard&Itemid=129&url=/articles/aa/abs/2008/30/aa10013-08/aa10013-08.html|author=Bean, J.L. ''et al.''|journal=Astronomy & Astrophysics|title=A Hubble Space Telescope transit light curve for GJ 436b|year=2008|access-date=2021-12-31|archive-date=2010-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100408055429/http://www.aanda.org/index.php?option=article&access=standard&Itemid=129&url=%2Farticles%2Faa%2Fabs%2F2008%2F30%2Faa10013-08%2Faa10013-08.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>這顆行星也可能是一個[[超級地球|超級地球]]。<ref>{{cite journal| url=http://www.iop.org/EJ/article/0004-637X/673/2/1160/21924.html | title=Ocean Planet or Thick Atmosphere: On the Mass-Radius Relationship for Solid Exoplanets with Massive Atmospheres | author=E. R. Adams, S. Seager, and L. Elkins-Tanton | journal=[[The_Astrophysical_Journal|The Astrophysical Journal]] | volume=673 | issue=2 | pages=1160–1164 | doi=10.1086/524925 | bibcode=2008ApJ...673.1160A|arxiv = 0710.4941 |date=February 2008}}</ref>

天文學家使用[[史匹哲太空望遠鏡|史匹哲太空望遠鏡]]測量格利澤436b的[[亮度溫度|亮度溫度]]，並發現這顆行星的大氣可能存在熱化學不平衡。他們得出這顆行星的大氣含有豐富的[[一氧化碳|一氧化碳]]，並缺乏[[甲烷|甲烷]]。這個結果是出乎意料的，因為天文學家們認為其甲烷濃度應比一氧化碳高。<ref>{{cite journal|url= http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v464/n7292/full/nature09013.html|title= Possible thermochemical disequilibrium in the atmosphere of the exoplanet GJ 436b|journal= Nature|volume= 464|pages= 1161–1164|date= 22 April 2010|arxiv= 1010.4591|bibcode= 2010Natur.464.1161S|doi= 10.1038/nature09013|access-date= 2013-12-15|archive-date= 2011-09-27|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110927085537/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v464/n7292/full/nature09013.html|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>[http://planets.ucf.edu/research/exoplanets/GJ436b-Wheres-the-methane GJ436b - Where's the methane?] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100514162550/http://planets.ucf.edu/research/exoplanets/GJ436b-Wheres-the-methane |date=2010-05-14 }} Planetary Sciences Group at the University of Central Florida, Orlando</ref><ref name=Knutson>{{cite journal| title=A ''Spitzer'' Transmission Spectrum for the Exoplanet GJ 436b |year=2011| last1=Knutson | first1=Heather A.| doi=10.1088/0004-637X/735/1/27| journal=Astrophysical Journal| volume=735, 27 |arxiv=1104.2901 |bibcode = 2011ApJ...735...27K }}</ref><ref name=Line>{{cite journal| title=Thermochemical and Photochemical Kinetics in Cooler Hydrogen Dominated Extrasolar Planets |year=2011| last1=LINE | first1=Michael R. | last2=VASISHT | first2=Gautam| last3=CHEN | first3=Pin| last4=ANGERHAUSEN | first4=D.| last5=YANG  | first5=Yuk L.| journal=Astrophysical Journal| arxiv=1104.3183| doi=10.1088/0004-637X/738/1/32|volume=738, 32|bibcode = 2011ApJ...738...32L }}, abstract in the arXiv titled "Thermochemistry and Photochemistry in Cooler Hydrogen Dominated Extrasolar Planets: The Case of GJ436b"</ref>

